  "prompt": "When did Jaime and Cersei become lovers?",
  "response": "Jaime and Cersei Lannister, characters from George R.R. Martin's \"A Song of Ice and Fire\" series and the HBO series \"Game of Thrones,\" became lovers when they were quite young. According to the backstory provided in the series, they first became intimate when Jaime visited Cersei at Casterly Rock after completing his knighthood training. This event is said to have occurred when Jaime was around 15 or 16 years old, and Cersei was about 16 or 17. Their relationship developed from there, continuing in secret due to the incestuous nature of their affair, which is taboo in their society.",
